{"tid":2050491,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"日本記者實測本能寺進軍路線","createTime":"2020-06-04T07:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T15:20:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cac397ab77478c3a6e3c8b5dcbef3b773b6af4eb","tid":2050491,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"這篇報導是京都新聞的三名記者，實際走一次明智光秀軍當年進攻本能寺的路線，出發時間也與光秀軍相同，大約晚上十點。<br />\n <br />\n午後10時   JR亀岡駅（亀山城跡附近）出發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NcNIIM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNcNIIM2.jpg&h=5dd124d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 亀山城跡旁的明智光秀像<br />\n <br />\n午後10時半 沿舊山陰街道向東<br />\n <br />\n午後11時   篠村八幡宮（亀岡市篠町）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qRvOpzr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqRvOpzr.jpg&h=77c7ac82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此地也是當年足利尊氏舉兵打倒鎌倉幕府之地。<br />\n <br />\n午後11時半 經過王子神社（亀岡市篠町）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lualp67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flualp67.jpg&h=56a77c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n午前０時   走老ノ坂的越嶺道路，到達老ノ坂隧道　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lAEM2ud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlAEM2ud.jpg&h=6bbb5774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n午前０時半 穿過隧道，繼續走國道９號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dbJNSRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdbJNSRz.jpg&h=0ca43434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n午前１時   過了老ノ坂向下，再度轉往舊山陰街道，到了與國道九號的樫原秤谷十字路口，已經看得見洛中的燈光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QGbaWDL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQGbaWDL.jpg&h=134af167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n午前２時　 在西京區的樫原十字路口前，偶然發現寫有「明智川」的駒札，是附近的用水路。傳說明智光秀在進軍本能寺途中，在此落馬，村民在幫他的同時，趁機提出希望能解決當地用水不足的請求，雖然三日天下的光秀不太可能幫村民解決用水問題，但可感受到光秀與領民的親近之感（實際是信長在更以前下令修築的水路<br />\n　　　　　 　<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/r00Qwsw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr00Qwsw.jpg&h=4048b8d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n午前３時   通過桂離宮，來到桂川<br />\n傳說這裡是光秀決心打倒信長，有名的那句話的發令場所<br />\n <br />\n記者三人也用盡全力大喊：「敵は本能寺にあり！」<br />\n <br />\n當時的桂川應該沒有架橋<br />\n從桂橋往西北方看，在黑暗中隱約能看到愛宕山的影子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5pDA7ql.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5pDA7ql.jpg&h=c1960856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳說光秀在曾在山頂的愛宕神社祈求能戰勝信長。<br />\n <br />\n午前４時　 氣溫下降，記者三人又冷又疲累，腳步越來越沉重<br />\n<br />\n走七条通向東，再走西洞院通北上，快到蛸薬師通的時候聽到小鳥的啾啾聲<br />\n <br />\n午前５時　 東邊的天空開始微亮，抵達目標的「本能寺跡」石碑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GxGHPhn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGxGHPhn.jpg&h=ed3aacf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從亀岡駅前的明智光秀像前出發，經過七小時<br />\n手機的計步器大約三萬七千七百步，走了大約二十五公里<br />\n <br />\n光秀軍接下來才是本番，但記者們已經沒有進攻本能寺的體力了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kyoto-np.co.jp/articles/-/257341?page=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyoto-np.co.jp%2Farticles%2F-%2F257341%3Fpage%3D2&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=0a46acb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kyoto-np.co.jp/articles/-/257341?page=2</a>"},{"pid":"60e15d8c7eea651e5362d6bf23e5a6ae8cbe97cb","tid":2050491,"uid":167721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"有冇二萬八千里長征實測<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ea99cadbe0916bb6415f031233179c3de36593","tid":2050491,"uid":64073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"行隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72567a5d68